--- linux-2.4.1-ac8.orig/drivers/media/radio/radio-maxiradio.c	Fri Feb  9 15:55:03 2001
+++ linux-2.4.1-ac8/drivers/media/radio/radio-maxiradio.c	Fri Feb  9 15:56:55 2001
